metadata.name: Twin of Chaos
metadata.description:
In your mind there is a world which is a fantasy world. that can imagine and create things But when your mind is confused and different opinions arise. The world will be divided into 2 sides, where the two heads are like minds on both sides with different and conflicting opinions. causing chaos and chaos But beneath this chaos, there is still one heart that sustains this conflict and chaos. There are many chains to hold the mind. To prevent this chaos from destroying your mind.

3467 x 4429 px
